reviewText: Whatre doing reading this review? You see what the others are saying. Add this to your collection now.
I have always loved this series and I misplaced Round 5. This DVD was exactly what I needed to complete my collection again :)

I love this DVD. This DVD has the most character development on it of all the DVDs currently available. There still is plenty of action though so don't worry. The 3rd episode on this DVD is my favorite. Its packed with great action and story. Plus this DVD sets up the next one perfectly and will make you want to buy Round 6.
